{
  "text": "The pre-treatment WBC and differential counts were evaluated at admission before conservative therapy. The post-treatment counts evaluated taken 7 days later after conservative therapy was adopted. The NLR was calculated by dividing the absolute neutrophil count by the absolute lymphocyte count [CITATION_1] .",
